author: Sheena McGinley
title: Gossip | Pic: Look who was on the pull in Panti Bar the other night!
text:
Antony Cotton just can't get a night off from pulling those pints, poor chuck.
Corrie's hardest working character (he only stitches knickers in the fact'ray by day, and pulls halves by night, while also keeping the local vicar happy) dropped by Panti Bar the other night before heading off to the premiere of The Queen of Ireland.
The Rover's Return's loss is Pantibar's gain.
Posted by Panti Bliss / Pantibar on Thursday, October 22, 2015
Sadly Antony wasn't sporting one of Sean's trademark shirts for the occasion, but he did bust out quite the leather number for the premiere.
